Product Description Brand New - Unused Parts Top Quality, Generic Aftermarket Part - Includes (8) Carbon Brushes as pictured Item

Specifications: It is always best to replace both brushes, even if only one is worn. Worn brushes frequently are the cause behind a motor running poorly. Replacing brushes can fix a motor that's operating intermittently.
New brushes can restore a motor's electric braking. When replacing carbon brushes, be sure to inspect your armature for burns, cracks, or other damage which can indicate larger motor problems.
Fits the following DeWalt models: D28402, D28110, D28112, D28401N New, Bulk Packed. replacement part. Consult owners manual for proper part number identification and proper installation.
